answers.answer: Congrats! So, do you think out was the castor oil, your medical scare or just your time?

I didn't try the castor. it was my bp that caused to induce. Didn't have preeclampsia but pressure was high and was dialated 4cm at prenatal appointment. Once broke waters at 1008 by 11p I was at 10cm but baby was still high. The pushing to get her down was tiresome. So happy pregnancy stage is over!!!
Oh ok...so many mommies, I'm getting these post confused!

question: Born @ 223am 6lbs8oz 18 inches long. She is beautiful!!! born @ 38 weeks exactly. I am so happy and blessed. Thank you ladies for your support and good luck :)
title: She's here!!!
